{"tid":1672363,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【興德前校長案】律政司申請覆核敗訴 維持原判陳章萍脫罪","createTime":"2019-10-24T05:19:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T05:33:09.000Z","uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b54745c91014f0acf862773202ebaa68bd854239","tid":1672363,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T05:19:29.000Z","msg":"屯門興德學校前年爆出一連串校政醜聞，時任校長陳章萍被指涉向教育局出示虛假員工面試記錄，受審後認為獲裁定一項使用虛假文書罪罪脫。律政司不服裁決申請覆核聆訊，原審水佳麗裁判官今天在屯門裁判法院裁定，控方沒有充足指控證明陳章萍透過虛假面試記錄隱瞞教育局職員，宣佈維持原判，亦批准辯方的訟費申請。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官坦言雖然陳章萍並非完全沒有可疑，但控方無法證實陳章萍有任何動機，去故意製作涉案虛假的文件，或在文件上簽署。而應徵者的供詞也支持，記錄上的面試確實曾經發生。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1120612/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E8%88%88%E5%BE%B7%E5%89%8D%E6%A0%A1%E9%95%B7%E6%A1%88-%E5%BE%8B%E6%94%BF%E5%8F%B8%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E8%A6%86%E6%A0%B8%E6%95%97%E8%A8%B4-%E7%B6%AD%E6%8C%81%E5%8E%9F%E5%88%A4%E9%99%B3%E7%AB%A0%E8%90%8D%E8%84%AB%E7%BD%AA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1120612%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E8%2588%2588%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E5%2589%258D%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E9%2595%25B7%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E5%25BE%258B%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%258F%25B8%25E7%2594%25B3%25E8%25AB%258B%25E8%25A6%2586%25E6%25A0%25B8%25E6%2595%2597%25E8%25A8%25B4-%25E7%25B6%25AD%25E6%258C%2581%25E5%258E%259F%25E5%2588%25A4%25E9%2599%25B3%25E7%25AB%25A0%25E8%2590%258D%25E8%2584%25AB%25E7%25BD%25AA&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUoWINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=2c5ab413\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1120612%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E8%2588%2588%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E5%2589%258D%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E9%2595%25B7%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E5%25BE%258B%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%258F%25B8%25E7%2594%25B3%25E8%25AB%258B%25E8%25A6%2586%25E6%25A0%25B8%25E6%2595%2597%25E8%25A8%25B4-%25E7%25B6%25AD%25E6%258C%25